content:
ISLAMABAD, July 18 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif Monday expressed his deep grief and sorrow over loss of 19 precious lives after a boat ferrying a number of passengers capsized in the River Indus, near Rahimyar Khan.
On his Twitter handle, the prime minister prayed for the departed souls and for the bereaved families to bear the losses with equanimity.
